== Definition ==
'''INT''' text_flags = 0

'''Text_flags''' is a [[global variable]]. When a [[dynamic text]] is created ([[write]](), etc), its [[flags]] value will equal the value of '''text_flags''' at the moment of creation. The default value is 0.

